Now, the upcoming process is initial inner judging, and I would like to ask all of Kabuku members for a help.
1. Click the link below and open the spreadsheet.

2. Check the entries, and select 10 of your favourite designs by entering “1”. For your information, on top of the sheet, there is a link to see the thumbnail list and a link for the contest if you want to revise the criteria.
3. Make sure you have selected 10 entries. You can check this with the calculated figure down at the very bottom.
I have done my own part, so please refer this as an example. Of course, feel free to ask if you have any questions.
After collecting feedbacks from everyone, the top 15 entries will move on to the final round, where they will be judged by the organizer, and the assigned juries.
And last but not lease, the most important information: Deadline is 10th Sept 18:00.
Please make sure to finish this in time.
